# NPM Registry Configuration for VT Code
#
# This file configures npm to publish the vtcode package to GitHub Packages
# For npmjs.org publishing, use environment variables or npm config commands
#
# For GitHub Packages, ensure GITHUB_TOKEN environment variable is set with:
# - write:packages (to publish packages)
# - read:packages (to download packages)
# - repo (to link packages to your repositories)

# Configuration for GitHub Packages registry (recommended for this project)
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${GITHUB_TOKEN}

# Scoped registry configuration
@vinhnx:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com